long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
How good are you at parking cars! Choose the car you want, complete dozens of fun puck levels and experience the adventure. There are four different racing cars in Car Parking Master. All racing cars are unlocked, so you can choose the car you want and complete the parking game levels. There are twenty-five parking tasks, each more difficult than the other, waiting for you in the Car Parking game.

The main objective of the car parking master game is to reach the finish line as soon as possible without hitting the surrounding pontoons. As the pontoons are more frequent in the advanced levels, you must use the cameras while parking the car. After checking that your car is inside the parking area from all angles, the level will be completed automatically, and the locks will be opened for you to pass to the next level.

How To Play
You can move your racing vehicle and deliver it to the parking area using the arrow keys. You can switch to other camera angles and experience a better car parking simulation using the C key. Since you have the right to crash three times, you must deliver your vehicle to the parking area in a controlled manner.

Car Parking Master Game Features
✓ Realistic graphics
✓ 10+ Level
✓ 3+ Car
✓ Change camera
✓ Realistic control

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Car Parking Master Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
